[SHORT DESC]
Causes damage to the enemy whenever they switch.

[LONG DESC]
<p>Does 12.5% damage with one layer, 16.67% damage with two layers, and 25% damage with three layers to the enemy when they switch in a new Pok√©mon. Is removed from opponent's side of the field when they use Rapid Spin. Only grounded Pokemon are affected. Hits through Wonder Guard.</p>

<p>Grounded Pokemon are Pokemon that are not part Flying, do not have Ingrain active, do not have the ability Levitate, and do not have Magnet Rise active. If Gravity is active, all Pokemon are grounded. All Pokemon holding an Iron Ball are grounded.</p>

<p><a href="/dp/articles/entry_hazards">Smogon has an article on this topic.</a>